Interface Book


  • public interface Book
    Book represents the unique copy of a Book. Books could have different underlying formats in the future. (e.g. AudioBook, ...)

    (this Interface is what someone who uses the API sees, when internally BookCopy objects are used)

    FOR DEMONSTRATION PURPOSES ONLY,
    AND MAY BE SUBJECT TO CHANGE
